      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·唐風·010.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">有杕之杜.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>有杕之杜，生于道左。彼君子兮，噬肯適我。中心好之，曷飲食之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>There is a solitary russet pear tree,
Growing on the left of the way.
That princely man there !
He might be willing to come to me.
In the centre of my heart I love him,
But how shall I supply him with drink and food?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
