      <prop type="x-translation-ref">有杕之杜.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>有杕之杜，生于道周。彼君子兮，噬肯來遊。中心好之，曷飲食之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>There is a solitary russet pear tree,
Growing where the way makes a compass.
That princely man there!
He might be willing to come and ramble with me.
In the centre of my heart I love him;
But how shall I supply him with drink and food?</seg>
      </tuv>
